lead_paragraph: A dropped stroke at the last hole could not prevent Thorbjorn Olesen extending his overnight lead from six to seven shots after the third round of the $7 million Turkish Airlines Open in Antalya on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Olesen Seven Clear Despite Late Blip in Turkey
